To make this "academic-ready" for an IT committee, your next step should be defining the Specific Objectives. In an IT thesis, these usually follow a pattern:
Analyze the current manual methods and challenges of informal workers in your target area.
Design a mobile-first architecture that integrates WhatsApp API for low-data communication.
Develop the platform (the "artifact") using your chosen stack (e.g., React Native, Flutter, or a Web App).
Evaluate the socio-economic potential through user feedback or a prototype test.
For your technical documentation, you can find excellent guides on WhatsApp Business Platform integration via the Meta for Developers portal to see how your app will actually "talk" to the workers.
